[{"id":598900,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1567062424","description":"用了 3 年的 y50，今天晚上屏幕的 A 壳和 B 壳突然裂开了，我现在都不敢合上屏幕，感觉屏幕壳子整个都要裂开了。<br /><br />平常只撸代码，不玩游戏了，自己对笔记本硬件不大了解，有老哥推荐合适的吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598900","replies":40,"created_ts":1567861494,"created":"21:04:54","title":"笔记本 GG 了，老哥们都是用什么本撸代码的？","author":"fengpan567","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fengpan567","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1317aa48a9ab0f096fc00da732594817?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":598911,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1567062424","description":"发现有的是从两边往上秃，有的是从中间往上秃，你是哪种秃？有何规律<br /><br /><br /><br /><br />#程序员<br />#秃顶美学","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598911","replies":39,"created_ts":1567866117,"created":"22:21:57","title":"做程序员的你，秃顶是从中间往上秃，还是两边往上秃？","author":"default7","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/default7","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/653c4003a7997bf1df7ae24f32b4aee9?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":598880,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1567062424","description":"<p>得益于高校的图书馆门禁以及我对知识的渴求\n我想利用树莓派做一个具备如下功能的机器：\n复制校园卡的门禁信息，仅用于图书馆刷卡，不作他用；（取之有道取之有道，我要的是知识，可是高校行政不认账，给钱也不让进，有些高校可以给钱办个临时卡，这种高校就良心。加之我发现不少高校图书馆平时空荡荡的，我一般看书是直接坐书架地上，不占用座位，所以请大家不要仇视渴求知识的少年）\n树莓派本身可以刷图书馆门禁；</p>\n<p>以上是我希望实现的，希望大家帮助我。\n可以提供关键词，我自主找资料学习制作，主要想了解树莓派实现这一功能的可能性。谢谢大家。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598880","replies":35,"created_ts":1567852209,"created":"18:30:09","title":"如何用树莓派做一个能够复制校园卡刷卡进入图书馆的机器","author":"Poto","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Poto","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0302c7c129487958b0423f4a4244500e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":598866,"node":"求职","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/cv","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2d6c/c4b2/507_mini.png?m=1564717597","description":"<p>在上海，说要带简历，我拿了都没有叫我拿出来，基本上都会提前打印。</p>\n<p>而深圳呢，面试全部都会问有没有带简历，无一例外，黑人问号</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598866","replies":35,"created_ts":1567846715,"created":"16:58:35","title":"深圳好像面试都要带简历","author":"nnegier","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/nnegier","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/00b9dc80a372050eec8fbfa5200a6186?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":598774,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1567062424","description":"部门要整私有云存储,要支持 EB 级别数据量, 请教下技术选型.<br /><br />目前了解到的开源方案主要是 Ceph, 但 ceph 坑也多, 求有经验的大佬指点","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598774","replies":35,"created_ts":1567821275,"created":"09:54:35","title":"私有云存储开发","author":"jeffreyji666","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jeffreyji666","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/157d/6c76/54383_mini.png?m=1448251948"},{"id":598857,"node":"罗技","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/logitech","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d709/f38e/370_mini.png?m=1567844454","description":"才用了几个月，快速移动的时候就开始卡顿了。然后在网上搜了一下，不是个例（搜索关键词 G903 stutter / G903 lagging ）。貌似是硬件上的 sensor 问题。<br /><br />暂时不想买罗技的任何鼠标了。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598857","replies":34,"created_ts":1567841905,"created":"15:38:25","title":"罗技的 G903 是一款令人失望的产品","author":"Livid","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Livid","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_mini.png?m=1553581155"},{"id":598884,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1567062424","description":"新换成了华威手机，自带得百毒输入法辣鸡得呀皮。求一个好用的手机断输入法。一是大字联想要方便，二是不要有广告。之前在小米用搜狗输入法，一堆广告给我恶心到了。<br /><br /><br /><br />以上这段子就是我用百度输入法大出来的…","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598884","replies":33,"created_ts":1567854373,"created":"19:06:13","title":"迫于辣鸡百度输入法，求个好用的手机端输入法","author":"tinycold","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/tinycold","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1f9a/3e5b/220057_mini.png?m=1494492425"},{"id":598849,"node":"硬件","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1564963417","description":"刚刚入手了一个全新的豆子峡谷，运行了一会发现外表发热，感觉散热不好，考虑要不要退货了。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598849","replies":31,"created_ts":1567839216,"created":"14:53:36","title":"有正经用过 NUC 的朋友吗？","author":"xing393939","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xing393939","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9096/5ec7/18925_mini.png?m=1418653049"},{"id":598821,"node":"奇思妙想","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ideas","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6353/8fe6/519_mini.png?m=1537099731","description":"<p>准备做一个产品死亡目录的网站。原型图已经画好了，最近在找 ui 的朋友做设计，有朋友做后端支持，我和一个朋友负责产品与运营工作，现在需要一个前端，有想做的朋友吗？</p>\n<p>项目介绍：\n项目灵感来源于 killed by google （ <a href=\"https://killedbygoogle.com/），国内有朋友业余时间做了一个\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://killedbygoogle.com/），国内有朋友业余时间做了一个</a> killed by bat。但上面都只是简单的产品列表。我想做的是产品死亡目录，主要是一些大家所熟知的产品，比如：近两年挂掉的熊猫直播，即刻，一罐等等。如果你认识这些产品，对这些产品有感情，可以给产品点蜡烛，留言等。后面还有很多功能，感兴趣的可以私聊。</p>\n<p>ps：该产品大概率是并没有得到验证，大概率是一个伪需求。所以并没有任何酬劳，就是想实现自己的一些想法，和大家一起创造点有趣的东西。</p>\n<p>有兴趣了解详细内容的朋友，可以添加我 wx：zacchen1314</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598821","replies":31,"created_ts":1567831635,"created":"12:47:15","title":"在准备做一个产品死亡目录的网站，需要前端，有想参与的朋友吗？","author":"zacfire","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zacfire","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3436b27017bbd6fc83d643839712233f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":598879,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1567062398","description":"最近选手机，5G 就暂时不考虑，价格定 3000 左右，配置上定个 855+的 CPU，android 最近好像也没啥好机子，oneplus7pro 855 半年也没掉多少价。看到魅族 16s Pro、IQOO Pro、nubia3S 或 z20，哪个更好？ IQOO Pro 4G 电池容量貌似挺大的，手机续航感觉才是最需要考虑的，其次是系统 UI 体验了。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598879","replies":30,"created_ts":1567852003,"created":"18:26:43","title":"魅族 16s Pro、IQOO Pro、nubia3S 或 z20 哪个更好些？","author":"Oysmart","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Oysmart","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1509/97f2/354561_mini.png?m=1562239845"},{"id":598860,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1566353744","description":"<p>100M 的带宽，iStat Menu 显示下载网速稳定&lt;10k/s，PAC/Global 模式开启均无效。第 4 次手机打开小火箭，开热点给电脑连接，终于达到 100k/s。结果 clone 到 66%时，速度又变成 0，并且静止 5 分钟了。我太难了。。。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598860","replies":30,"created_ts":1567843286,"created":"16:01:26","title":"我太难了！想从 GitHub 上 clone 一个项目下来，失败了 3+1 次。。","author":"charlieputon","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/charlieputon","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3b8c55c2da0ff20d0341fd0f2053d2d8?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":598831,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1566353744","description":"<p><strong>有什么成熟的能够穿透移动 NAT 的解决方案</strong></p>\n<p>常有和朋友远程互传大文件的需求，因为各种原因（文件大小、速率要求、便捷性），网盘方案基本排除了，于是就看看能不能利用一下自己的对等宽带（只有百兆），直接 P2P 传输文件。</p>\n<p>有尝试过 <a href=\"https://github.com/fatedier/frp/blob/master/README_zh.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">Frp</a> 测试性的 xtcp，但是穿透失败；<a href=\"https://file.pizza/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FilePizza</a> 速度不理想，甚至不如度盘的速度；以及<a href=\"https://worksphere.cn/transfer\" rel=\"nofollow\">SimpleFiler</a> ,穿透失败；</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>frp 经过服务器的方式，因为服务器水管太小，拿来传文件不现实</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/edwardwohaijun/file-transfer\" rel=\"nofollow\">FileTransfer</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598831","replies":30,"created_ts":1567834724,"created":"13:38:44","title":"P2P 大文件传输解决方案","author":"Bwoywan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Bwoywan","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/69cb/7908/410868_mini.png?m=1561911726"},{"id":598863,"node":"Python","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/python","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8613/985e/90_mini.png?m=1565780301","description":"<p>求助个问题，最近做的一些网站部署完以后第一次打开网站超级慢，应该与服务器无关，之后再打开就很快了，这个问题找了很久没找到答案，网站是 python+react。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598863","replies":28,"created_ts":1567844037,"created":"16:13:57","title":"用 Python 写的网站前端用 react 首次打开网站超级慢","author":"chiva","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/chiva","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a4523f047ced49830245fc5d7c8646b7?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":598763,"node":"深圳","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1559027827","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598763","replies":28,"created_ts":1567817163,"created":"08:46:03","title":"出差深圳，哪里可以玩？","author":"yeshiwei","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yeshiwei","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f5c5/9267/10147_mini.png?m=1356101415"},{"id":598757,"node":"YouTube","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/youtube","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/ea5d/2f1c/64_mini.png?m=1528870075","description":"刚发现 YouTuBe 的广告变 30s 了，不能跳，只能完整看完。记得之前的长广告都是能跳过的啊，这是最近才改的吗？<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qhl1970.png\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qhl1970.png\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/598757","replies":28,"created_ts":1567792013,"created":"01:46:53","title":"YouTuBe 强制播放 30 秒广告","author":"jakiepaper","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jakiepaper","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fd53/4ba2/66824_mini.png?m=1404426359"}]